The paper deals with the problem of knowledge base completion, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed model involves embedding entities and relations into low dimensional spaces, which is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of type constraints, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR).
